{"tid":2154479,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"《異動股》壹傳媒（２８２）插近４１％，據報證監已展開調查","createTime":"2020-08-13T07:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T07:25:49.000Z","uid":118880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4599a06d978d007858dc7c5d6adfc93853d45520","tid":2154479,"uid":118880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:03:25.000Z","msg":"13/08/2020 14:24<br />\n<br />\n《經濟通通訊社１３日專訊》壹傳媒（００２８２）跌４０﹒７７％，報０﹒３８５元；成<br />\n交約５﹒０６億股，涉資２﹒３６億元，主動沽盤５６％。集團股價連跌兩日累挫６５％。<br />\n  據本地傳媒引述消息人士指，過去兩日證監會及聯交所就壹傳媒不尋常股價及成交量變動向<br />\n個別證券業界查詢，並索取客戶資料、交易紀錄等。消息人士坦言，監管機構行動迅速，雖然他<br />\n們向來有就股份異動進行查詢，在證券界內亦非「新鮮事」，惟過往通常事後才進行。<br />\n  再度被萬華媒體（００４２６）減持的毛記葵涌（０１７１６）亦跌２３﹒２３％，報０﹒<br />\n７６元。<br />\n<br />\n會唔會停牌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b406bd0cf1dddea951a123369527782f0025e605","tid":2154479,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:05:41.000Z","msg":"炒股都唔比"},{"pid":"46ab0cef7d951e9e1b6bc92c883f23196c7a35f6","tid":2154479,"uid":136994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8cf0aac4ea33f07d7324f723832dfa2dd85079","tid":2154479,"uid":263198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:11:01.000Z","msg":"如果停牌<br />\n手持股票會點？"},{"pid":"ddab5fbb905dbbb04c6b5de7c768d3d8609870e5","tid":2154479,"uid":252985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa8cf0aac4ea33f07d7324f723832dfa2dd85079","tid":2154479,"uid":263198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:11:01.000Z","msg":"如果停牌<br />\n手持股票會點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:12:18.000Z","msg":"無野既 無得場內交易住姐"},{"pid":"32cdea78f82acc976c21080b0142c07d7dbdb68d","tid":2154479,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo